videos.description: Donovan Mitchell helps extend Louisville's early lead with a chance at a four-point play.
videos.headline: Louisville's Mitchell hits three and gets fouled

videos.description: Mangok Mathiang demonstrates good help defense skills by swatting the Georgia Tech shot away.
videos.headline: Louisville's Mathiang denies Georgia Tech opportunity

videos.description: Josh Okogie flies through the lane for the putback dunk to cut into the Louisville lead.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Okogie tries to spark comeback with dunk

videos.description: Josh Okogie finds Ben Lammers for the easy dunk, as Georgia Tech tries to get a run going.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Lammers throws it down off nice pass

videos.description: Louisville's Quentin Snider darts through the lane for the lay-in to put the Cardinals up double digits with under three and half minutes remaining.
videos.headline: Louisville's Snider finds opening for lay-in

videos.description: Off the miss, Anas Mahmoud soars over everyone for the huge two-handed put back dunk to push Louisville's lead back to double-digits.
videos.headline: Mahmoud flies over everyone for massive put back jam
